<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A typical Calgary suburban neighborhood, Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill shares its boundaries with the Trans Canada Highway on the north and the Crowchild Trail on the west. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The Hounsfield Heights/Briar Hill Real Estate offers its residents convenient access to the stylish Kensington District, Bow River pathways and city downtown. </p>

